cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.DC, cs.PF 

This paper discusses monitoring network state, which is a topic related to computer networks and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses data analysis and algorithms, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper mentions the GEANT2 high-speed academic network, which is a distributed computing infrastructure, making categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.PF (Performance) also likely.
